    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer4072613350" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer5082647843533699004">Tozer did a great job of attempting to describe our indescribable God. He didn’t waste a word seeking to communicate the attributes of God. Although we won’t be able to understand a Holy, perfect God and his infinitude. This book allowed me to worship and wonder about the Creator of it all. I recommend this book to anyone, but be warned you’ll probably finish this book with more question and confusion than when you started. It definitely stirred my affections for God and allowed me to sit in His</span>
  <span id="freeText5082647843533699004" style="display:none">Tozer did a great job of attempting to describe our indescribable God. He didn’t waste a word seeking to communicate the attributes of God. Although we won’t be able to understand a Holy, perfect God and his infinitude. This book allowed me to worship and wonder about the Creator of it all. I recommend this book to anyone, but be warned you’ll probably finish this book with more question and confusion than when you started. It definitely stirred my affections for God and allowed me to sit in His Greatness and Perfection.</span>
  <a data-text-id="5082647843533699004" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
